track_notes: Just a little track to the summit while going to visit some friend. Easy walk and very nice sight, but to not walk too close of the edge, on north part, it is very deep!!!
Winter walk, starting from the Lure Ski Resort because of the road closed you must walk in snow, this is not difficult nor long. enjoy the place, more info at FIVI Jerome
Jerome F4IVI and Yl have walked more than 18km, as the road was closed for winter time! More info @F4IVI
